          "x": 524,
          "y": 0,
          "name": "Panel",
          "context": "We are to nest SVGs inside of these boxes, from the carbon pack. one for delete probably in the bottom, one for opening the control panel (the top one, and when opened, it gets that blue color to show active state and active open panel). one for updating the component, so clicking there should open a popover or modal which we will work on later, and later decide what is updatable - maybe re-bind to another component from the system etc. not sure yet, but some sort of update/config alternative. And anything else that you can think of that might be smart. render the svgs at 16x16px inside the boxes.\n\nThis one always sits top right 12px right from the active frame",
