            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "Y9lv7W",
              "name": "LoginScreen-default-final",
              "context": "<!--\n## LoginScreen-default-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** default\n**Component:** LoginScreen\n\n### Purpose\nUnified entry point at /login. Two OAuth options (GitHub primary for connectors, Google for viewers). Signing with either lands the user on /.\n\n### Design notes\n- Surface: page bg #f6f6f9, card surface #ffffff, radius 16, 1px #dfe0e7.\n- Typography: Geist 24/500 headline, Geist 14 #6d6467 subhead, Geist 12 #9b9295 legal.\n- AuthButton variants live in Dashboard-Components-Kit (AuthButton-github-default-final, AuthButton-google-default-final).\n- GitHub button is dark (#121111 fill / white text). Google button is white surface with #dfe0e7 border. Both 44px tall, radius 14.\n- Google sign-in is enough to view shared instances. Connecting a repo on /connect prompts to link a GitHub identity if the user came in via Google (per dashboard-build-plan.md auth flow split).\n\n### For AI agents\n- Demonstrates the only screen reachable while signed-out.\n- After auth, route to / which is Dashboard-empty-final (zero repos) or Dashboard-populated-final.\n- Do not add password / email fields. OAuth only.\n-->",
              "width": 1440,
              "height": 900,
              "fill": "#f6f6f9ff",
              "cornerRadius": 16,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#dfe0e7"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "justifyContent": "center",
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "V1osn",
                  "name": "Login-Card",
                  "width": 480,
                  "fill": "#ffffffff",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#dfe0e7"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 32,
                  "padding": [
                    40,
                    40,
                    32,
                    40
                  ],
                  "alignItems": "center",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "C1xC9g",
                      "name": "Login-Brand",
                      "gap": 10,
                      "alignItems": "center",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "HuKjq",
