              "id": "F5CjB",
              "name": "connLabel",
              "fill": "#9b9295",
              "content": "05 / Connect repo",
              "lineHeight": 1,
              "fontFamily": "Geist",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "500"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "y6krPp",
              "name": "ConnectRepo-default-final",
              "context": "<!--\n## ConnectRepo-default-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** default (one repo selected)\n**Component:** ConnectRepo\n\n### Purpose\nThe /connect flow. Pick a GitHub installation, pick a repository, choose which workspace owns it, and submit (build plan lines 132, 141, 188–190).\n\n### Design notes\n- Surface: page bg #f6f6f9, form panel #ffffff with radius 16 + 1px #dfe0e7.\n- Two-column form, single panel. Sections: GitHub installation → Repository → Workspace assignment → Footer.\n- 'Step labels' use Geist 11/500 #9b9295 uppercase tracking, mirroring the STATE label pattern from variant-toggle-final on the canvas.\n- Repo rows use Geist Mono 14 for org/repo. Selected row has #f6f6f9 fill + filled radio.\n- Workspace radio cards mirror RepoRow workspace chips: Personal (dot + label), Team Acme (mono initial avatar + label).\n- New repos default to Personal per build plan line 132 — this layout shows a user changing the destination to Acme.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Sibling state variants live in component kit (ConnectRepoForm-{state}-final).\n- Cancel returns to /. Connect repo returns to / and adds the new RepoRow at the top of the list with status 'Syncing… initial build'.\n- Google-only users hit a blocking link-GitHub modal here (not shown in this layout).\n-->",
              "clip": true,
              "width": 1440,
              "height": 900,
              "fill": "#f6f6f9ff",
              "cornerRadius": 16,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#dfe0e7"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "vCJOF",
                  "type": "ref",
                  "ref": "KJinn",
                  "name": "connTb"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Jvwmy",
                  "name": "ConnectRepo-Main",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "height": 836,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 24,
                  "padding": [
                    40,
                    80
                  ],
                  "alignItems": "center",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "DmADk",
                      "name": "ConnectRepo-Crumb",
                      "width": 720,
                      "gap": 6,
                      "alignItems": "center",
